  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is a no frills hotel! Just a place to lay your head at the end of a long day of activity. Get involved in adventurous hikes and bike excursions in the Valtellina mountains, then come back to a laid-back and friendly atmosphere at the end of the day.</p>]]></listingDescription>
