  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> are about 21m² and sleep up to three people. They're decorated in a modern mountain lodge style. They have a minibar, balcony with mountain views, TV, fridge, safe, shower and a hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> also have a balcony and are perfect for solo travellers.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
